## API Endpoints Reference

All endpoints follow your existing pattern: `/make-server-8c22500c/financial/*`

### Connection Management

- `POST /financial/stripe-create-session` - Start Stripe flow
- `POST /financial/stripe-save-accounts` - Save connected accounts
- `POST /financial/plaid-create-token` - Start Plaid flow
- `POST /financial/plaid-exchange-token` - Exchange Plaid token

### Data Access

- `GET /financial/accounts?userId={uuid}` - Get linked accounts
- `GET /financial/balances?userId={uuid}` - Get current balances
- `GET /financial/transactions?userId={uuid}&limit={n}` - Get transactions

### Management

- `POST /financial/disconnect-account` - Disconnect account
- `GET /financial/debug-config` - Check configuration

### Webhooks

- `POST /financial/stripe-webhook` - Stripe webhook receiver

